cu.explanation_en: Setting the second integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the RU clock source to an unknown enum 'invalid' will cause hardware synchronization failures and prevent proper RU operation.
du.explanation_zh: 將 RU 時鐘源設定為未知的枚舉值 'invalid'，會導致硬體同步失敗，並阻止 RU 正確運作。
